manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: NO MORE CLUTTER Effortless storage meets elegant design – our knife set comes with high-quality pine wood wooden base, allowing you to neatly organize and store your knives in a drawer. Experience the convenience of easy access and a clutter-free kitchen, all while adding a touch of sophistication with the high-quality pine wood base.

DISHWASHER SAFE Crafted with convenience in mind, these knives can effortlessly withstand dishwasher cycles, ensuring a hassle-free and time-saving experience. Enjoy the ease of maintaining your knives pristine condition without compromising on performance.

Sharp Blade Precision crafted with Japanese high carbon stainless steel blades, our knife set boasts exceptional sharpness, durability, and corrosion resistance. Elevate your culinary experience with blades that effortlessly slice through ingredients, ensuring precision and longevity in every cut. High Quality Handle This knife set gives you superior blades with ergonomic non-slip ABS handles. Sharp, sturdy & practical. No rust, stains or pitting here! Each handle is triple riveted for greater durability Seamless Design Perfection Knife set features handles and blades crafted from a single piece, ensuring unparalleled durability and a seamless, stylish aesthetic. Experience the ultimate in precision and control with a unified construction that effortlessly combines form and function. High Quality Pine Wood Blocks Knife storage blocks are made of high-quality pine wood and are designed to store and protect your cutlery. The block includes rubber feet for stability.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 11, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars ok nice handles
reviews.reviewText: I like the handles on these, they seem very sturdy. The knives are sharp out of the box. They are advertised as high carbon Japanese stainless steel. I can't speak to that, they don't seem exceptionally sharp. They are holding their edges after a couple days of use, but it's too soon to know longevity in that respect. If premature, I will definately update. They are made in China, which is clearly marked in the advertisement.The holder is nice especially if you want to store in a drawer.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 12, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Compact and organized
reviews.reviewText: This knife set comes with a knife block and a 6 piece knife set. There is an 8" chef knife, 8" bread knife, 6.5" Santoku knife, 5' utility knife and a 3.5" paring knife. The knife set has ergonomic handles, razor sharp edges and precision blades made by Katisun. They have a nice weight to them, easy to handle and great for cutting. I'm happy to recommend this set of knives with the knife block.
